1
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:41,260
上帝!
Jesus!

2
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:44,400
"致旧金山市府.
"To the city of San Francisco.

3
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:48,210
"我十分乐意每天干掉一个人...
"I will enjoy killing one person every day...

4
00:05:48,210 --> 00:05:51,340
"...直到给我10万美金.
"...until you pay me one hundred thousand dollars.

5
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:54,540
"如果没问题,请在明天早上...
"If you agree, say so tomorrow morning...

6
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,830
"...旧金山时报登个私人启示...
"...at personal column, San Francisco Chronicle...

7
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,170
"...到时我回合你们联络.
"...and I will set up meeting.

8
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,070
"如果我没有收到你们的回话...
"If I do not hear from you...

9
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,850
"...我将十分乐意再干掉一个天主教的牧师或者一个（黑鬼）...
"...it'll be my next pleasure to kill a Catholic priest or a...

10
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,910
"...蝎子."
"...Scorpio."

11
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:14,440
他们究竟在想些什么?
What goes on in their minds?

12
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:16,450
疯子.
Kooks.

13
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:20,410
他到底想让我到哪去筹集10万美元呢?
Where the hell does he expect me to find a hundred thousand dollars?

14
00:06:20,410 --> 00:06:23,930
市长先生,你不会想付钱给他吧？
You're not thinking of paying him, are you, Mr. Mayor?

15
00:06:25,420 --> 00:06:29,550
旧金山市府不会同罪犯妥协的.
The City of San Francisco does not pay criminals not to commit crimes.

16
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:32,480
相反,我们会把钱花在警察局.
Instead, we pay a police department.

17
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:35,350
局长,谁负责这个案子？
Chief, who's in charge of this case?

18
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,260
科拉汉探员,他正在外面等候.
Inspector Callahan. He's outside.

19
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:45,050
叫科拉汉探员进来.
Send Inspector Callahan in.

20
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,020
科拉汉？
Callahan?

21
00:06:51,810 --> 00:06:53,840
市长先生,他就是科拉汉探员..
Mr. Mayor, Inspector Callahan.

22
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:54,960
好的.
All right.

23
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,350
让我们谈谈吧.
Let's have it.

24
00:06:58,020 --> 00:07:00,510
- 谈什么? - 你的报告.你调查到了什么？
- What? - Your report. What have you done?

25
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,280
在过去的45分钟...
For the past 3/4 hour...

26
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:06,180
...我一直在你的办公室外傻等.
...I've been sitting in your outer office waiting on you.

27
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:10,110
小心点,哈里. 要知道你在和市长先生说话.
Damn it, Harry. It's the mayor you're talking to.

28
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:15,630
我们能坐下来谈么,克拉汉探员.
Won't you sit down, Inspector Callahan?

29
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,480
已经有一个女士死了！
There's a madman loose.

30
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:31,780
我已经问过你进展得怎么样了？ 难道还不够么？
I've asked you what's being done. Fair enough?

31
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:38,280
我们已经派一组人鉴定档案.
We've got a dozen men checking identification files.

32
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:41,910
调查每一个有案底的勒索者. 梁上君子...
Checking on all known extortionists, rooftop prowlers...

33
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,380
...枪手,偷窥者...
...rifle nuts, peepers...

34
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,900
市长先生?
Mr. Mayor?

35
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:48,530
我们已经在屋顶部署了人员 还安排了直升机...
We've arranged for rooftop surveillance and helicopters...

36
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:52,060
...尤其在天主教堂和学校附近...
...especially around the Catholic churches and schools...

37
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,890
...还有黑人聚集区.
...and in the black area.

38
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,390
武器专家正在鉴定子弹.
Ballistics is checking on the slug.

39
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,690
我们已经确认型号是30-60.
We're sure it's a 30-06.

40
00:07:58,690 --> 00:08:01,490
七条膛线,右手螺旋....
Seven lands and grooves, right-hand twist...

41
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,910
我们正在用计算机搜集...
We're running a computer check...

42
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:07,680
...所有出生在...
...on everybody in the files whose birthday falls between...

43
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,210
..9月21日和10月23日之间的人的名单..
...October 23 and November 21.

44
00:08:09,210 --> 00:08:10,270
为什么？
Why?

45
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:12,620
因为这些人的星座是天蝎.
Natives of Scorpio.

46
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,340
谢谢你,探员..
Thank you, Inspector.

47
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,660
你们向外界透露这些了吗？
Mention this note to anyone?

48
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,430
你呢？
How about you?

49
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,110
没有.
Nobody.

50
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:26,980
你的妻子,情人,还有媒体?
Your wife, sweetheart? Press?

51
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:28,280
没有.
Nobody.

52
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:34,890
好吧,让媒体放风.
All right. Give the message to the Chronicle.

53
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:38,510
就说我们会付钱 但是这么多钱需要时间.
We'll pay. But we need time to get the money together.

54
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:40,570
等一下.你的意思是？
Wait a minute. Do I get this right?

55
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,640
你想耍花招？
You'll play this creep's game?

56
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,760
这将给我们喘息的时间.
It'll give us breathing space.

57
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,780
但这会害死其他人的.
It might get somebody killed.

58
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:49,830
让我会会这个杂种！
Let me meet with the son of a bitch!

59
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:53,460
不,不会这样的 那才真会已一场惨剧收场.
Nope, none of that. It would end up with a real bloodbath.

60
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:56,550
我同意局长的意见. 我们就这样做.
I agree with the chief. We'll do it this way.

61
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,700
谢谢你的赏脸,市长阁下. 来吧,探员,我们走.
Thank you, Mr. Mayor. Come on, Callahan, let's go.

62
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:09,960
我不希望你去年 在菲尔莫制造的灾难重现.
I don't want trouble, like you had last year in the Fillmore district.

63
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,000
先生
sir？

64
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,810
哈里
harry

65
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,590
知道么？这是原则.
understand？That's my policy.

66
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:16,590
当一个男子追一位妙龄少女...
When an adult male is chasing a female...

67
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:20,930
并想强奸时,开枪是我的职责.
...with intent to commit rape, I shoot the bastard. That's my policy.

68
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,870
准备？
Intent?

69
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:24,500
你怎么会那么认为？
How did you establish that?

70
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:31,030
当一个裸体男人在小巷里追一个女人, 上举刀下举棍,嘿嘿..
When a naked man chases a woman in an alley with a knife and a hard-on...

71
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:34,430
我认为这种人是 不会为红十字会筹款的.
...I figure he isn't out collecting for the Red Cross.

72
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,880
他说的对.
I think he's got a point.

73
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:38,360
-汉拉克探员 -杰非
- Inspector Callahan. - Jaffee.

74
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,470
谢谢
thanks

75
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,150
照旧.
Usual.

76
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:43,650
是照旧的午餐还是晚餐?
Usual lunch, or usual dinner?

77
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:45,200
有什么不同么？
What difference does it make?

78
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,050
没什么.
Not much.

79
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:51,150
嗨,杰斐...
Hey, Jaffee...

80
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:55,520
那个褐色福特轿车 还停在银行前面的吗？
...is that tan Ford still in front of the bank?

81
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:58,110
褐色福特轿车？
Tan Ford?

82
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:03,480
是的,褐色福特.
Yeah, tan Ford.

83
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:05,060
没熄火？
Engine running?

84
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:09,120
我不知道,我怎么知道？
I don't know. How can I tell?

85
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:12,700
- 看看排气管冒黑烟么？ - 嗯,真恶心.
- Exhaust fumes out of the tailpipe. - That's awful!

86
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,950
看那些烟？
Look at that pollution.

87
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:18,750
哦？

88
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:21,970
你能帮个忙么？
Do me a favor, will you?

89
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,680
打这个电话
Call this telephone number.

90
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,100
警察局？
Police Department?

91
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,200
告诉他们克拉汉探员认为...
Tell them Inspector Callahan thinks there's a...

92
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:33,360
有人正在银行抢劫,明白听清了么？
...two-eleven in progress at the bank. Got it?

93
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,420
听清了么.
Got it.

94
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:40,110
一定要告诉他们正在抢,懂么？
Be sure and tell them it's in progress, right?

95
00:11:40,110 --> 00:11:41,270
正在抢.
In progress.

96
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:42,530
是的,先生.
Yes, sir.

97
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:51,310
现在,他们就等着警察来吧.
Now, if they'll just wait till the cavalry arrives.

98
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:55,980
妈的!
Shit!

99
00:12:10,820 --> 00:12:11,810
站住!
Halt!

100
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:38,260
我知道你在想什么.
I know what you're thinking.

101
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:42,060
"这个人是开了六枪还是五枪？"
Did he fire six shots or only five?

102
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:46,590
说实话,由于兴奋我忘了数.
To tell the truth, in all the excitement I've kind of lost track myself.

103
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:49,720
但我拿着这把44毫米口径的转轮手枪 世界上威力最大的手枪，
But since this is a.44 Magnum, the most powerful handgun...

104
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:52,010
...可以完全打爆你的头情况下...
...and would blow your head clean off...

105
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:56,730
...你该问问自己 "我今天走运么？"
...you've got to ask yourself one question: "Do I feel lucky?"

106
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:58,540
哦.你觉得呢？渣滓?
Well, do you, punk?

107
00:14:20,380 --> 00:14:22,440
我想知道.
I got to know.

108
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:42,360
狗娘养的!
Son of a bitch!

109
00:14:46,530 --> 00:14:49,090
不错,哈里,看来这条腿还有救.
It looks like we can save that leg.

110
00:14:49,090 --> 00:14:50,960
为了生活没办法.
I've got a couple under my knee.

111
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,760
考虑换个别的工作？
Ever consider another line of work?

112
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:56,030
我十分感谢你的建议斯蒂芬.
I really appreciate this, Steve.

113
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,640
当然.我们乡下小子总该同舟共济的.
We Potrero Hill boys have to stick together.

114
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,640
面对现实吧.
Nothing fancy, now.

115
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:04,390
用镊子涂一点药水就够了.
Just a little tweezers and Mercurochrome.

116
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:07,450
我有去到到警察局 教你如何逼供犯人吗？
Do I tell you how to beat a confession out of a prisoner?

117
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:12,210
- 我过界了. - 你或许会有些不舒服.
- I haven't got all night. - You might experience discomfort.

118
00:15:12,210 --> 00:15:15,870
如果那样,就让你妻子帮...
But if you do, just have your wife fix a...

119
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:18,140
对不起,哈里.
Sorry, Harry.

120
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:20,110
你用那个做什么？
What will you do with those?

121
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,660
把你的裤子剪开.
Cut your pants off.

122
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:24,500
-不,我们还是把它脱了吧. - 那会弄伤你的.
- No. We'll pull them off. - It'll hurt.

123
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:27,030
为了节约 $29.50, 就痛点吧.
For $29.50, let it hurt.

124
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:29,620
你可以转过身,如果觉难堪的话.
You can turn your back if you're embarrassed.

125
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:55,500
- 早上好,探长.. - 你好,麦瑞.
- Good morning, Inspector. - Maria.

126
00:17:04,320 --> 00:17:05,100
当然！
yeah！

127
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:03,250
你要见我么,长官？
You wanted to see me, Lieutenant?

128
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,870
你究竟打算什么时候去剪发？
When the hell you going to get a haircut?

129
00:17:10,020 --> 00:17:11,920
你去剪的时候.
Whenever you do.

130
00:17:12,080 --> 00:17:16,180
谁有空？ 我一直在寻找线索到凌晨三点.
Who's got time? I was up till 3 a.m. Checking the search patterns.

131
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:19,750
- 都花在加班上了. - 要干一天的..
- Put in for overtime. - That'll be the day.

132
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:22,360
你做的不错. 局长很满意.
You made a good pinch. Chief was pleased.

133
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:25,520
- 他很满意？ - 是的,他说你做的很棒.
- He was? - He wanted me to tell you: "Well done!"

134
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:27,960
我真是感动得一塌糊涂.
I can't tell you how moved I am.

135
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,530
顺便说一下
I pass along a compliment...

136
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:34,680
你可以有礼貌一点 说句谢谢又不会死.
...you could be a little polite. It might not kill you to say thanks.

137
00:17:34,900 --> 00:17:36,860
如果升我的职,我会说的.
I'd rather say thanks to a raise.

138
00:17:36,860 --> 00:17:41,220
哈里,你的电话. 芝加哥来得. 一个武器专家的.
Harry, check communications. Something from Chicago. A gun nut.

139
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:44,690
- 我马上来 - 等一下!
- I'll get right on it. - Now wait a minute!

140
00:17:44,690 --> 00:17:46,250
我给你找了个搭档.
I'll put somebody with you.

141
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,200
你说什么？
What are you saying?

142
00:17:54,060 --> 00:17:55,490
你需要一个搭档.
You need a partner.

143
00:17:55,490 --> 00:17:58,660
- 我原来的呢? - 他住院了!
- What's wrong with the one I've got? - He's in the hospital!

144
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:02,960
- 他会马上出院的. - 跟奇克刚则斯打个招呼.
- He'll be out in a few weeks. - Say hello to Chico Gonzales.

145
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:05,790
- 他将和你一起办案. - 你一定在开玩笑.
- He'll be working with you. - You must be kidding.

146
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:08,250
我没时间训练新手.
I have no time to break in newcomers.

147
00:18:08,250 --> 00:18:11,450
- 为什么你不帮帮这个小伙子？ - 什么意思？
- Why don't you do this boy a favor? - What do you mean?

148
00:18:12,100 --> 00:18:16,040
你知道和我搭档的人都是什么下场， 塔兹克现在住在医院...
You know what happens to guys I worked with. Deitzick's in the hospital...

149
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,520
...范度奇死了..
...and Fanduchi's dead.

150
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:18,780
所以?
So?

151
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:23,770
所以，如果我要一个搭档 我会找一个有经验的.
so I need a partner, I'll get me one who knows what he's doing.

152
00:18:23,770 --> 00:18:24,960
让迪乔奇干怎么样?
What about DiGeorgio?

153
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,490
没门！
No way!

154
00:18:26,970 --> 00:18:29,240
要么你和冈萨雷斯工作 要么你就别干.
You work with Gonzales or you don't work.

155
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:31,300
这是来自15楼的命令,明白了？
Straight from the fifth floor. Got it?

156
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:35,440
明白了.
I got it.

157
00:18:39,970 --> 00:18:42,330
看到迪乔奇,叫他过来.
If you see DiGeorgio, send him in here!

158
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:45,750
你是本地人?
You from around here?

159
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:48,100
是的,但是我去过圣何塞州.
Yeah, but I went to San Jose State.

160
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:51,910
- 打球么？ - 不,我打拳,是轻量级的..
- Play ball? - No, I boxed. Light heavyweight.

161
00:18:51,910 --> 00:18:54,880
我就需要你这样的大学生.
Just what I need is a college boy.

162
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:58,840
- 发现了我身上的优点了？ - 这才哪到哪.
- Found anything you like about me yet? - It's early yet.

163
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:01,610
- 有学位？ - 社会学.
- Get your degree? - Sociology.

164
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:06,930
- 社会学！如果命大,你还有能学到很多. - 我会的.
- Sociology! You'll go far, if you live. - I intend to.

165
00:19:06,930 --> 00:19:09,120
我是克拉汉探长.
Inspector Callahan.

166
00:19:09,300 --> 00:19:13,060
别让你在大学学的条条框框害死你 我很可能也因此被你害死.
Don't let your degree get you killed. I'm liable to get killed with you.

167
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:14,420
收到.
I'll remember that.

168
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:20,200
- 英雄,昨天你干的真棒. - 胖子,长官要见你.
- Hero! Nice work yesterday. - Fatso! Bressler wants to see you.

169
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,600
哈里,你真是个好人.
You're a sweet man, Harry.

170
00:19:27,580 --> 00:19:30,350
探长.我想问个问题.
There is one question, Inspector Callahan.

171
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:32,710
为什么大家都叫你硬汉哈里.
Why do they call you Dirty Harry?

172
00:19:33,050 --> 00:19:34,880
那是我们哈里的一个特点.
That's one thing about our Harry.

173
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:36,550
冷酷无情.
Doesn't play favorites.

174
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:41,520
哈里,讨厌每个人. 英国佬,爱尔兰佬,新西兰佬, 意大利,黑人,白人,中国佬...
Harry hates everybody: Limeys, micks, hebes, dagos, niggers, honkies, chinks.

175
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,810
凡是你能想到的,他都不喜欢.
You name it.

176
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:47,030
- 那么,墨西哥人呢? - 自己问他!
- How does he feel about Mexicans? - Ask him!

177
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,830
我最不喜欢.
Especially spics.

178
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:45,810
看,有个人在屋顶上!
Hey! There's a guy on the roof over there!

179
00:22:45,810 --> 00:22:47,840
在华盛顿广场的斯托克顿街.
On Stockton Street by Washington Square.

180
00:23:12,120 --> 00:23:13,310
你,屋顶上的!
You, on the roof!

181
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:15,160
就是你.
You, there!

182
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,960
你,站住!你在干什么?
Yes, you. Stop what you're doing.

183
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:19,430
转过身把手举起来.
Turn around and put your hands in the air.

184
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:40,390
我真不明白直升机怎么回放走他!
I don't know how the helicopter boys lost him!

185
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:43,820
他们怎么眼睁睁看着他跑了?
How could they let him get out without seeing him?

186
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:48,000
他们只说没做，正如所料.
They were probably talking instead of looking, like they were supposed to.

187
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,590
有可能.
That's possible.

188
00:23:57,740 --> 00:24:00,870
-所有单位请注意. - 把声音开大点.
- Attention, all units. - Turn that thing up louder.

189
00:24:00,870 --> 00:24:04,500
嫌犯最后一次出现在华盛顿广场附近.
Prowler last seen in the vicinity of Washington Square.

190
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:07,280
嫌犯是一个成年男子..
He is an adult male.

191
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:11,980
白种人.重复一遍,成年男子,白种人.
Caucasian. Repeat, adult male Caucasian.

192
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:14,310
据最后目击,他手提褐色皮箱...
When last seen, he was wearing tan chinos...

193
00:24:14,310 --> 00:24:18,180
...身穿白蓝色汗衫,棕色外套 或毛衣,戴着黑色手套.
...pale blue shirt, brown coat or sweater, dark gloves.

194
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:19,580
他带着一个褐色皮箱...
He had a tan suitcase...

195
00:24:19,580 --> 00:24:23,920
...有可能装着30-06来复枪.他正被通缉...
...which probably contains a 30-06 rifle. He's wanted...

196
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:27,320
这帮蠢才! 他们可以把所有人都抓回去了!
Those loonies! They ought to throw a net over the whole bunch!

197
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:29,020
我明白你的意思
I know what you mean.

198
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,440
看那!
There!

199
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,130
怎么了?
What?

200
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:35,820
褐色皮箱.
Tan suitcase.

201
00:24:36,540 --> 00:24:37,300
哪?
Where?

202
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:38,600
看不见了.
I lost him.

203
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:42,410
他在那,就是那儿.
There he goes, over there.

204
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:44,120
是褐色的皮箱么?
Does that bag look tan?

205
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:46,580
我不知道 我连他的影都没找到.
I don't know, I haven't even seen him yet.

206
00:24:46,580 --> 00:24:48,240
在路口左转.
Go to Filber and hang a left.

207
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,270
小心别撞到他们!
Look out for these people!

208
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:51,100
喂,你没长眼睛.
Hey,Fruitcake!

209
00:24:51,100 --> 00:24:53,230
别挡道,蠢才!
Get out of the way, hammerhead!

210
00:24:58,080 --> 00:25:01,570
是褐色的,我知道肯定是.
It was a tan suitcase. I know it was.

211
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,470
我看见了
I saw him.

212
00:25:05,220 --> 00:25:06,880
- 他在那. - 我看见了.
- There he is. - I see him.

213
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,790
二号车, 车牌号是...
Car 2, the license number...

214
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:14,660
...10-32 雪弗来, 克莱拉多州牌照.
...at 10-32 on that Chevrolet, Colorado plates.

215
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:23,580
- 你要怎么做? - 你再找条路.我从这进去
- How do you want to work this? - Find another way in. I'll go in here.

216
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:26,450
二号车, 那辆雪弗来是什么型号?
Car 2, what's the model of that Chevrolet?

217
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:31,870
二号车. 是自动档黑斑马.
Car 2. It's an Impala convertible.

218
00:25:31,870 --> 00:25:33,140
10-4.
10-4.

219
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:49,750
你可以取消行动,10-25. 已有三辆车在那了.
You can cancel that 10-25. Three cars here.

220
00:26:12,560 --> 00:26:14,290
有人在家么?
Anybody home?

221
00:26:34,930 --> 00:26:36,960
你给我带礼物了?
Did you bring me a present?

222
00:26:37,570 --> 00:26:39,160
让我看看.
Let me see it.

223
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,810
它太漂亮了.
It's beautiful!

224
00:26:59,810 --> 00:27:02,940
为什么你不买个好点的装蛋卷的罐子？
Why don't you go get a nice container of egg rolls?

225
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:08,340
你大饱眼福了?
You getting an eyeful?

226
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:10,730
你这个该死的杂种!
You goddamn pie hawker!

227
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:14,510
- 我们应该叫警察来. - 我就是警察...
- We should call the police. - I am a police...

228
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,190
都住手.

229
00:27:22,280 --> 00:27:24,310
举起手来,靠到墙上, 马上,快！
Up against the wall. Right now! Move.

230
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,400
放他们走吧. 让他们走？
Let them go.

231
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:32,680
你听见了.
You heard me.

232
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,460
他们殴打了一位长官.
They assaulted a police officer.

233
00:27:34,620 --> 00:27:37,810
一个警察？ 他站在桶上偷看...
A police officer! He was standing on a can peeking in...

234
00:27:37,810 --> 00:27:39,780
...性感的玛丽和他的男朋友.!
...on Hot Mary and her boyfriend!

235
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,570
闭嘴.马上离开.
Beat it. Get out of here.

236
00:27:46,520 --> 00:27:49,650
- 那个拿箱子的人呢? - 我们搞错了.
- How about the man with the suitcase? - Wrong number.

237
00:27:50,800 --> 00:27:52,790
我刚才想起一件事.
I just had another thought.

238
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:55,070
哦？想到什么?
Yeah? About what?

239
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:57,560
为什么大家叫你硬汉哈里？
About why they call you Dirty Harry.

240
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:06,160
71号探员.71号探员.
Inspector 71.

241
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:11,860
71号探员,请回话.
Inspector 71. Please respond to your call.

242
00:28:11,860 --> 00:28:14,230
71号探员,你收到了？
Inspector 71. Do you read me?

243
00:28:14,230 --> 00:28:17,860
- 我是71好探员. - 8-0-4已经在处理.
- This is Inspector 71. - I've got an 8-0-4 in progress.

244
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:20,520
地点是波土街的加利福尼亚大楼.
California Hall at Polk and Turk streets.

245
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:22,320
10-4,我们马上去.
10-4. We're on our way.

246
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:43,330
又是一个傻瓜.
It's some idiot.

247
00:28:43,330 --> 00:28:45,270
在哪？我怎么看不见.
Where? I don't see him.

248
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:50,620
- 就那 - 哦,我看见了..
- There he is. - Yeah. Now I see him.

249
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:57,020
我已叫了10-29和 10-28.
I have a 10-29 and a 10-28.

250
00:28:57,020 --> 00:29:00,350
在贝克600区. 在雪弗来车上.
In 600 block of Baker. On a Chevrolet.

251
00:29:00,350 --> 00:29:05,180
加利福尼亚牌照. 道格,查理,维克 4-7-2.
California license. D-dog, C-Charlie, V-Victor 4-7-2.

252
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:18,800
我们本以为他是那个杀手,没想到 是个要跳楼的人.
We thought it was your sniper, but it turned out to be a suicide attempt.

253
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:36,110
- 有人和他谈过了? - 是的,但是没用,不过你在这就好了...
- Anybody try to talk him down? - Yeah, no luck. But now you're here...

254
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:39,250
- 你要我上去.. - 太感谢了.
- You mean, I go up. - We'd sure appreciate it.

255
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:45,820
看他要上去, 看到了么? 他会摔死的!
Look at him go, will you? He's going to get hurt!

256
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:53,250
不要企图救我!
Don't you try to get me!

257
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:58,790
我才不.是你想死.不是我.
Not me. You're the one who wants to get yourself killed. Not me.

258
00:30:59,140 --> 00:31:02,740
你们这些家伙总是这样.. 最后关头你们总想...
Always happens with you guys. The last minute you want to...

259
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:08,170
抓住个伴，你跳下去吧.我可不想.
...grab onto somebody, take somebody with you. Down you go. Not me!

260
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:10,420
你不想救我?
Won't you try to grab me?

261
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:16,710
几年前，我的一个朋友到20层楼 去救一个想跳楼的.
A friend of mine was up about 20 floors with a jumper a few years ago.

262
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:19,010
那个疯子抓住他 把他也带了下去.
The jumper grabbed him and they went off.

263
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:20,180
摔碎在一起
Mashed all over.

264
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:24,930
分辨不出谁的脚是谁的 谁的手是谁的.....
Couldn't tell which legs was with which, which arms with which...

265
00:31:25,140 --> 00:31:28,440
简直惨不忍睹.. 我告诉你, 我几乎恶心死了.
It was a terrible mess. I tell you, I almost threw up myself.

266
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:31,920
- 我上来只是想知道你的名字和住址. - 为什么?
- I'd just like your name and address. - Why?

267
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:34,660
等你下去后,会变得支离破碎!
It's such a mess down there afterwards!

268
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:39,990
根本无法确认你的身份. 即使找到你的驾照!
It makes identification impossible. Even if they find your driver's license!

269
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:41,940
也会被血泡碎!
All that blood!

270
00:31:44,020 --> 00:31:46,510
我想,我想我要吐了.
I think.I think I'm going to puke!

271
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:50,800
不要吐,宝贝. 底下那些人都在看着.
Don't do that, son. All those people down there looking up.

272
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:53,760
消防队长也在仰头看...
The fire chief looking up. With his face...

273
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,780
你这个杂种!
You rotten bastard!

274
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,440
把担架抬走.
Get the stretcher out here.

275
00:32:57,620 --> 00:33:02,490
现在你明白我为什么叫硬汉哈里了？ 每一件脏活都是这么解决的.
Now you know why I'm called Dirty Harry. Every dirty job that comes along.

276
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,960
71号探员.71号探员.
Inspector 71.Inspector 71.

277
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:21,090
我是71号探员
This is Inspector 71.

278
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:26,140
刚得到消息,在希尔和特斯街角 一个黑人男孩出事了.
Got something for you. Corner of Sierra and Texas. A young boy, Negro.

279
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:29,520
他怎么了？
What about him?

280
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:32,480
他被子弹打中面部,轰的四分五裂.
Shot in the face. Blew part of it away.

281
00:33:34,450 --> 00:33:36,420
确认死者身份了么?
Anybody know who the boy is?

282
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:38,950
他叫查理拉塞尔.
His name was Charlie Russell.

283
00:33:38,950 --> 00:33:40,480
我是他妈妈.
I'm his mother.

284
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:44,310
他才十岁.
He's only 10 years old.

285
00:33:58,240 --> 00:34:00,900
探长,这位长官... 哦,天呀!
Inspector, this officer... Oh, Jesus Christ!

286
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:03,100
你还是去安慰那位妈妈吧.
You'd better go check on the mother.

287
00:34:15,890 --> 00:34:17,020
你发现什么了么?
What do you have?

288
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:20,330
发现了30-05型的弹壳.
That 30-06 shell casing.

289
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,340
他应该就在这开的枪.
He was up here all right.

290
00:34:26,720 --> 00:34:28,590
那个坏蛋又犯案了.
Welcome to Homicide.

291
00:34:47,220 --> 00:34:51,420
为警察局设计这套蓝色制服的家伙...
The man who designed blue serge uniforms for police departments...

292
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:53,960
...现在不得不靠买这种刷子谋生了!
...has to sell these for a living!

293
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:02,050
448毫米的,大弹匣步枪?
.458 Magnum?

294
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:06,290
- 这能打死头大象了. - 是的.
- This thing will stop an elephant. - Yeah.

295
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:11,030
- 显然你只喜欢小型的. - 先生,我只有那些.
- Apparently you like a little edge. - All I can get, sir.

296
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:14,750
他不是大象,哈里. 他不是任何动物.
He's no elephant, Harry. He's no animal of any kind.

297
00:35:14,750 --> 00:35:16,410
你们发现什么了, 先生?
What have you got, Lieutenant?

298
00:35:16,410 --> 00:35:20,810
蓝色标识的地方今晚将有人巡逻.
The blue flags represent the units that are going to be on duty by dark tonight.

299
00:35:20,810 --> 00:35:23,140
- 两班倒,还开加班. - 尤其是晚上.
- Double shifts and overtime. - At nighttime.

300
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:26,010
白天有直升机,令他无法活动.
Daylight, the helicopters will keep him off the roofs.

301
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:31,120
我们尽量高调. 所有警员尽量引人注目。
We're going for high visibility. Units will make themselves very noticeable.

302
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:33,680
- 除了这块地区. - 对.北滩地区.
- Except here. - Right. The North Beach area.

303
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,380
把那里留他.
We're saving that for him.

304
00:35:36,340 --> 00:35:38,930
- 你知道在哪监视比较好? - 知道.
- Have you found a good stakeout? - I think so.

305
00:35:38,930 --> 00:35:42,960
就是昨天他们发现他的那个地方.
It's a building that overlooks the roof where they spotted him yesterday.

306
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:45,150
有什么问题么?
Something bothering you?

307
00:35:46,020 --> 00:35:46,850
没有.
Nothing.

308
00:35:46,850 --> 00:35:49,080
说吧. 这没外人.
Speak up. You're among friends here.

309
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:52,410
他再回到那个屋顶是不太可能的.
It seems a long shot that he'd come back to the same roof.

310
00:35:52,410 --> 00:35:55,540
在旧金山有那么多高楼
There are a lot of rooftops in San Francisco.

311
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:59,650
但是多数上屋顶的门已经被锁住了. 只有这个是给他留着的.
Most of them are locked. This particular one'll be open for him.

312
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:03,830
这些变态的家伙的行为是有规律的.
These sick guys have behavior patterns.

313
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:07,880
我们不是见过有些人总是去抢 同一条街上的商店3,4次.
We know they'll rob the very same store 3, 4 times in a row.

314
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:11,210
或许是在寻找某种变态的满足吧.
Must appeal to their superego or something.

315
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:13,760
蝎子又行动了.
Scorpio strikes again.

316
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,850
他们喜欢那种感觉.
They like that feeling.

317
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:19,750
还有一个理由令他选择同一个屋顶.
There's one other reason why he might pick the same rooftop.

318
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:22,940
能清楚地监视到圣保罗教堂.
He's got a clear view of the St. Peter and Paul's church.

319
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:25,060
而今晚教堂将举行弥撒.
And they're having a novena tonight.

320
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:27,570
还有呢.
Go on.

321
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:30,810
在纸条上他说要杀一个黑鬼和一个神父.
The note. He threatened to kill a priest or a Negro.

322
00:36:30,890 --> 00:36:32,550
那个男孩是个黑小子.
The Russell boy was black.

323
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:36,350
他将要兑现另一个目标--神父.
He may just figure he owes himself a padre.

324
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,900
这是71号探员.
Inspector 71.

325
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:57,440
我们已经到达了监视地点.
We're in position to start our surveillance.

326
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,840
神父怎么办?
How about the priest?

327
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:26,210
- 他知道自己是诱饵么? - 是的,他愿意做.
- He knows he's being set up for bait? - Yeah, he wanted to.

328
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:30,530
我们告诉他今晚将有人顶替他.
We told him we had a volunteer willing to take his place.

329
00:37:30,530 --> 00:37:31,690
谁?
Who?

330
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:35,160
你猜不到的.
Never guess.

331
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:39,300
嗯.我知道了 要静候凶手.
Yeah, I know. Welcome to Homicide.

332
00:39:09,700 --> 00:39:12,600
你有点亏待自己,哈里.
You owe it to yourself to live a little, Harry.

333
00:39:28,200 --> 00:39:30,490
