What am I going to tell him?

501
01:02:29,059 --> 01:02:31,459
就告诉他真相.
Why don't you start by telling him the truth?

502
01:02:31,459 --> 01:02:34,759
说是冈萨雷斯的上级让他这么做， 就是我.
Tell him Gonzales was obeying orders from a superior. Me.

503
01:02:35,059 --> 01:02:37,619
告诉他你什么都不知道.
Tell him you didn't know anything about it.

504
01:02:37,920 --> 01:02:41,450
当事情结束他如果想撤我的职 我没意见.
When this is over, if he wants my badge, he can have that too.

505
01:02:43,840 --> 01:02:46,600
你带酒了么?
You wouldn't have a belt of booze around here, would you?

506
01:02:53,560 --> 01:02:55,760
布莱斯勒副局长的办公室.
Lieutenant Bressler's office.

507
01:02:58,840 --> 01:03:00,740
- 找到他! - 发生什么了?
- Put him on. - What is it?

508
01:03:01,200 --> 01:03:06,430
是公园的急救中心, 他们刚诊治了一个受了腿伤的家伙.
It's Park Emergency. They just treated a guy who had a knife wound in the leg.

509
01:03:07,880 --> 01:03:10,900
是的,医生? 那个人长的什么样？
Yeah, doctor? What'd this guy look like?

510
01:03:11,619 --> 01:03:13,449
长长的金发...
Long blond hair...

511
01:03:13,859 --> 01:03:18,699
...中等身材, 大约150磅. 面色苍白.
...medium build, about 150 pounds. Pale complexion.

512
01:03:19,080 --> 01:03:22,700
- 医生,他说名字了么? - 没.
- He didn't give you his name, doc? - Nope.

513
01:03:23,760 --> 01:03:25,450
他们通常都给一个假名.
They usually give a phony name.

514
01:03:26,320 --> 01:03:28,280
但我在什么地方看过他.
But I've seen him someplace.

515
01:03:29,380 --> 01:03:33,540
你的线索很重要. 有一个女孩子就要窒息而死了.
It's important you remember. There's a 14-year-old girl who's suffocating.

516
01:03:33,540 --> 01:03:35,600
我再想想!我再想想!
I'm trying to think!

517
01:03:35,859 --> 01:03:37,259
在哪来着...
It was...

518
01:03:38,400 --> 01:03:39,990
我肯定他就在附近工作.
I believe he works around here.

519
01:03:39,990 --> 01:03:43,190
医生,能看看么?他很疼!
Doctor, could you give him something? He's in pain!

520
01:03:43,190 --> 01:03:44,850
好的,等等.
Yes, just a moment.

521
01:03:49,760 --> 01:03:51,250
孩子一个小时以后就要死了.!
She'll be dead in an hour!

522
01:03:51,250 --> 01:03:53,270
我在努力想!
I'm trying to remember!

523
01:03:55,299 --> 01:03:57,199
哦,我想起来了.
I've got who he is.

524
01:03:58,120 --> 01:04:02,320
当举行球赛的时候 他在那卖日程表.
When they had football, he used to sell programs at the stadium.

525
01:04:03,139 --> 01:04:05,939
我想是球场的守门人让他住那的.
I think the groundskeeper lets him live there.

526
01:04:06,140 --> 01:04:08,730
- 在哪? - 那.
- Live where? - There.

527
01:04:13,379 --> 01:04:15,009
卡泽球场.
Kezar Stadium.

528
01:05:19,450 --> 01:05:21,610
没有搜查证，要非法进入？
Illegal entry. No warrant.

529
01:05:22,380 --> 01:05:24,110
我们爬进去.
Looks like we climb.

530
01:05:25,420 --> 01:05:26,910
不太好爬.
Too much linguine.

531
01:05:28,160 --> 01:05:29,920
我再去找条路进去.
I'll find another way.

532
01:08:48,179 --> 01:08:49,199
别动!
Stop!

533
01:09:08,780 --> 01:09:11,980
别再开枪了! 你要杀了我!
Don't do anything more! You tried to kill me!

534
01:09:12,580 --> 01:09:13,710
你需要帮忙么?
You need any help?

535
01:09:16,419 --> 01:09:20,549
- 不关你事, 胖子. - 求求你了,不要开枪了!
- Go on and get some air, fatso. - Please! No more!

536
01:09:20,899 --> 01:09:24,429
你没看见我受伤了么? 你射中我了,不要再开枪了!
Can't you see I'm hurt? You shot me! Please, don't!

537
01:09:24,520 --> 01:09:26,720
我需要医生!
Let me have a doctor!

538
01:09:27,619 --> 01:09:30,089
我要医生! 请不要杀我!
Please, get me the doctor! Don't kill me!

539
01:09:30,380 --> 01:09:31,870
那孩子在哪?
The girl, where is she?

540
01:09:31,870 --> 01:09:33,170
你想杀了我？
You tried to kill me!

541
01:09:33,170 --> 01:09:37,370
如果我想,你的脑浆早就把这玷污了,孩子在哪?
If I did, your head would be splattered all over this field. Where's the girl?

542
01:09:38,400 --> 01:09:39,530
我要我的律师.
I want a lawyer.

543
01:09:39,530 --> 01:09:41,460
我问你,孩子在哪?
I said, where's the girl?

544
01:09:41,840 --> 01:09:43,360
我有权要一个律师.
I have the right for one.

545
01:09:43,360 --> 01:09:44,850
孩子在哪?
Where's the girl?

546
01:09:45,280 --> 01:09:48,510
我有权找律师!
I have the right for a lawyer!

547
01:09:48,510 --> 01:09:50,070
不,不要这样!
Don't! Please!

548
01:09:50,070 --> 01:09:52,040
我有权利. 我要我的律师!
I have rights. I want a lawyer!

549
01:11:32,340 --> 01:11:34,780
哈里-科拉汉. 有什么急事找我？
Harry Callahan. He said it was urgent.

550
01:11:34,780 --> 01:11:38,770
是的检察官有话和你说.
Yes, the district attorney has been wanting to talk to you.

551
01:11:38,770 --> 01:11:41,970
- 科拉汉探长到了. - 请他进来.
- It's Inspector Callahan. - Have him come in, please.

552
01:11:43,120 --> 01:11:45,350
请这边走.
Won't you come this way?inspector.

553
01:11:45,720 --> 01:11:49,120
- 你要咖啡么? - 不,谢谢.
- May I bring you in a cup of coffee? - No, thanks.

554
01:11:58,040 --> 01:11:59,800
我马上就好.
I'll be done in a minute.

555
01:12:00,300 --> 01:12:01,660
坐吧.
Have a seat.

556
01:12:05,740 --> 01:12:09,200
我仔细看了你的逮捕报告.
I've just been looking over your arrest report.

557
01:12:10,800 --> 01:12:14,140
将警察工作做的非常与众不同.
A very unusual piece of police work.

558
01:12:16,430 --> 01:12:17,690
令人惊讶.
Really amazing.

559
01:12:19,380 --> 01:12:20,540
我比较走运罢了.
I had some luck.

560
01:12:20,540 --> 01:12:24,440
你应该感到幸运我没有控告你谋杀!
You're lucky I'm not indicting you for assault with intent to commit murder!

561
01:12:27,320 --> 01:12:32,080
谁给你权力去私闯民宅和拷打犯人?
Where does it say you've got a right to kick down doors, torture suspects?

562
01:12:32,080 --> 01:12:36,140
拒绝提供医疗服务和法律援助, 你都干了些什么?
Deny medical attention and legal counsel? Where have you been?

563
01:12:37,120 --> 01:12:39,810
我以圣母之名，起誓.
Does Escobedo ring a bell? Miranda?

564
01:12:40,780 --> 01:12:43,140
你一定知道第四修正案!
You must have heard of the 4th Amendment!

565
01:12:45,820 --> 01:12:48,690
我要说的是,人都有权利.
What I'm saying is, that man had rights.

566
01:12:50,240 --> 01:12:53,000
我完全糊涂了,哪个人的权利？
I'm all broken up about that man's rights.

567
01:12:53,560 --> 01:12:55,960
你应该知道. 我告诉你个新消息.
You should be. I've got news for you.

568
01:12:55,960 --> 01:12:58,720
他已经离开医院了,他被释放了.
When he's well enough to leave the hospital, he walks.

569
01:13:00,230 --> 01:13:01,750
你说什么?
What are you talking about?

570
01:13:01,750 --> 01:13:02,910
他自由了!
He's free!

571
01:13:03,920 --> 01:13:05,220
你把他放了?
You're letting him go?

572
01:13:05,280 --> 01:13:07,040
我们必须那样做. 我们不能再扣留他.
We have to. We can't try him.

573
01:13:07,340 --> 01:13:08,670
为什么?
And why is that?

574
01:13:09,000 --> 01:13:12,030
我不能用50万元纳税人的钱...
Because I'm not wasting 1/2 million tax dollars...

575
01:13:12,030 --> 01:13:14,260
...去打一场不可能赢得官司.
...on a trial we can't possibly win.

576
01:13:14,440 --> 01:13:16,970
问题就是我们没有证据.
The problem is, we don't have any evidence.

577
01:13:17,600 --> 01:13:19,160
那些又是什么?
What do you call that?

578
01:13:19,160 --> 01:13:20,320
我说那些什么都不是.
I call it nothing.

579
01:13:20,930 --> 01:13:22,130
什么都不是.
Zero.

580
01:13:23,900 --> 01:13:27,660
你说专家认为子弹和枪不吻和?
You're saying that Ballistics can't match the bullet up to this rifle?

581
01:13:27,660 --> 01:13:30,720
专家说的算不了什么!
It does not matter what Ballistics can do!

582
01:13:31,000 --> 01:13:33,900
这把枪或许可以是个不错的收藏品.
This rifle might make a nice souvenir.

583
01:13:34,640 --> 01:13:37,270
- 但是不足以作为证据! - 谁说的?
- But it's inadmissible as evidence! - Who says?

584
01:13:37,660 --> 01:13:38,820
法律.
It's the law.

585
01:13:39,500 --> 01:13:41,020
法律一定是疯了!
Then the law is crazy!

586
01:13:42,140 --> 01:13:44,970
这是法院的检察长.
This is Judge Bannerman of the appellate court.

587
01:13:44,970 --> 01:13:49,970
他对宪法的了如指掌. 我咨询过他的看法.
He also holds classes in constitutional law. I've asked him for an opinion.

588
01:13:50,340 --> 01:13:51,400
你能谈谈?
Your Honor?

589
01:13:52,520 --> 01:13:57,430
据我所知这次搜查是违法的.
In my opinion, the search of the suspect's quarters was illegal.

590
01:13:57,980 --> 01:14:02,110
从而这些证据都是违法的...
Evidence obtained thereby, such as that hunting rifle for instance...

591
01:14:02,110 --> 01:14:04,100
...不足以作为证据.
...is inadmissible in court.

592
01:14:04,700 --> 01:14:08,690
我十分遗憾.你应该拿到搜查证再去的.
You should have gotten a search warrant. I'm sorry.

593
01:14:08,690 --> 01:14:11,920
- 就是这样. - 搜查证? 一个女孩子已经死了!
- It's that simple. - Search warrant? A girl was dying!

594
01:14:12,340 --> 01:14:15,310
根据医学报告，她确实死了.
She was, in fact, dead according to the medical report!

595
01:14:15,310 --> 01:14:16,610
但是我不知道这件事!
But I didn't know that!

596
01:14:17,140 --> 01:14:22,010
法院会同情警官对女孩的关心...
The court would recognize the officer's legitimate concern for the girl...

597
01:14:22,320 --> 01:14:26,560
...但不会因此宽恕他们施暴.
...but there is no way they can possibly condone police torture.

598
01:14:27,060 --> 01:14:30,690
所有关于女孩的证据如嫌犯的证词...
All evidence concerning the girl, the suspect's confession...

599
01:14:31,070 --> 01:14:32,360
...还有物证...
...physical evidence...

600
01:14:32,360 --> 01:14:34,630
...都不会被采纳.
...would have to be excluded.

601
01:14:40,600 --> 01:14:42,560
你能控告他么!
You can get him on something!

602
01:14:43,280 --> 01:14:46,240
没有了女孩和枪?
Without the evidence of the gun and the girl?

603
01:14:46,900 --> 01:14:49,660
我总不能控告 他在人行道上吐痰吧!
I couldn't convict him of spitting on the sidewalk!

604
01:14:51,220 --> 01:14:53,620
现在, 嫌犯的权利...
Now, the suspect's rights...

605
01:14:53,620 --> 01:14:55,490
...被亵渎了...
...were violated...

606
01:14:55,850 --> 01:14:58,050
...在第四第五...
...under the 4th and 5th...

607
01:14:58,050 --> 01:15:00,950
...或者是第六第十四修正法案下.
...and probably the 6th and 14th Amendments.

608
01:15:01,320 --> 01:15:03,880
那么那个女孩呢, 她的权利呢?
And Ann-Mary Deacon, what about her rights?

609
01:15:04,510 --> 01:15:07,570
她被强奸并死在了井里? 谁为她说话.
She's raped and left in a hole to die! Who speaks for her?

610
01:15:07,570 --> 01:15:09,190
区检察院办公室.
The district attorney's office!

611
01:15:09,920 --> 01:15:11,680
如果你愿意让我们做的话.
If you'll let us.

612
01:15:13,640 --> 01:15:17,740
我也有妻子和孩子. 我想把他抓起来的心情比你急切.
I have a wife and kids. I don't want him on the streets any more than you do.

613
01:15:18,260 --> 01:15:19,990
他不会子外面呆很久的.
He won't be out there long.

614
01:15:19,990 --> 01:15:22,220
你是什么意思?
What is that supposed to mean?

615
01:15:22,560 --> 01:15:25,590
不久他会打断自己的腿. 我会在现场.
Sooner or later he will stub his toe and I'll be there.

616
01:15:25,900 --> 01:15:28,530
这里不会容忍任何私刑的!
This office won't stand for any harassment!

617
01:15:29,040 --> 01:15:33,340
如果你认为这是他最后一次 你一定是疯了.他还会杀人的.
You're crazy if you think you've heard the last of him. He will kill again.

618
01:15:33,820 --> 01:15:35,310
你怎么知道?
How do you know?

619
01:15:36,500 --> 01:15:38,190
因为他热衷杀人.
Because he likes it.

620
01:18:05,680 --> 01:18:07,470
你肯定没人跟踪?
You sure you weren't tailed?

621
01:18:07,700 --> 01:18:08,920
是的.
Yeah.

622
01:18:34,060 --> 01:18:36,330
你真的要200美元的？
You really want $200 worth.

623
01:18:36,800 --> 01:18:38,700
是的.
Every penny of it.

624
01:18:53,580 --> 01:18:55,050
享受为你的服务吧.
Might as well be comfortable.

625
01:18:55,680 --> 01:18:57,300
来吧, 坐.
Go on, sit.

626
01:19:05,000 --> 01:19:06,430
别紧张.
Relax.

627
01:19:07,740 --> 01:19:09,670
放松.
Take it easy.

628
01:19:10,620 --> 01:19:12,950
都会好的.
It's going to be all right.

629
01:19:53,700 --> 01:19:55,970
你肯定你还要？
You sure you want the rest of it?

630
01:19:56,940 --> 01:19:58,700
给够每一分!
Every penny's worth!

631
01:20:00,400 --> 01:20:03,860
你这个黑狗!
You black son of a bitch!

632
01:20:25,600 --> 01:20:28,070
这是免费的.
This one's on the house.

633
01:20:42,500 --> 01:20:44,130
就是他.
That's got to be him.

634
01:20:48,260 --> 01:20:51,380
你说这是旧金山警局对你做的么?
Are you claiming that the San Francisco Police did this to you?

635
01:20:51,380 --> 01:20:52,940
我发誓. 上帝会给我作证.
I swear it. As God is my judge.

636
01:20:52,940 --> 01:20:55,100
为什么他们打你?
Why are they harassing you?

637
01:20:55,100 --> 01:20:57,580
他们要设计陷害我谋杀罪.
They tried to frame me with the murder.

638
01:20:57,960 --> 01:21:00,860
现在他们做到了. 看看我!
And now they're trying to murder me. And look at me!

639
01:21:00,860 --> 01:21:05,130
在我被证明有罪之前，我都是清白的. 但看看他们对我所做的一切.
I'm supposed to be innocent until proven guilty and look at what they did to me.

640
01:21:05,280 --> 01:21:08,550
我无论去哪他都跟着我. 监视我.
Everywhere I go cops follow me. And just look at me!

641
01:21:08,890 --> 01:21:11,820
等一会, 护士. 让我再问一个问题.
Just a minute, nurse. Let me ask him one more question.

642
01:21:11,820 --> 01:21:14,520
- 你知道谁揍得你么? - 是的.
- Did you see who did this to you? - Yes.

643
01:21:14,740 --> 01:21:15,970
你认识他?
Can you identify him?

644
01:21:16,380 --> 01:21:21,050
他是克拉汉.他是个警察 专业杀人犯.科拉汉.
His name is Callahan. He's a big cop. Works Homicide. Callahan.

645
01:21:22,800 --> 01:21:25,970
看,那是四点的新闻的重播.
Now, that's the reruns from the 4 o'clock news.

646
01:21:26,200 --> 01:21:29,200
他还在时报上登了个声明.
Since then he's given a statement to The Chronicle.

647
01:21:29,200 --> 01:21:32,500
他说你跟踪他并把他揍了.
He claims you've been following him. And beat him up.

648
01:21:33,460 --> 01:21:35,220
是那么回事么,哈里?
What about it, Harry?

649
01:21:36,640 --> 01:21:39,200
- 你要收我的勋章? - 我要你回答.
- You want my star? - I want an answer.

650
01:21:39,740 --> 01:21:41,500
你跟踪他了么?
Have you been following him?

651
01:21:42,740 --> 01:21:46,330
我下班后跟踪他.
Yeah, I've been following him on my own time.

652
01:21:46,330 --> 01:21:48,660
- 任何人都知道我没揍他. - 为什么?
- Anybody can tell I didn't do that. - How?

653
01:21:49,860 --> 01:21:52,660
因为他那样子还是太漂亮了 这就是为什么!
Because he looks too damn good, that's how!

654
01:21:53,280 --> 01:21:56,040
在你走之前 我们要讲明一件事.
Before I let you go, let's get one thing straight.

655
01:21:56,040 --> 01:21:58,770
不得再有监视行为!
I don't want any more surveillance!

656
01:22:00,000 --> 01:22:01,760
他也不得有.
Neither does he.

657
01:22:03,400 --> 01:22:04,460
什么意思?
What does that mean?

658
01:22:07,000 --> 01:22:08,620
晚安,先生.
Good night, sir.

659
01:22:11,540 --> 01:22:13,340
去,试试.
Go ahead. Try them.

660
01:22:14,520 --> 01:22:18,150
- 我经常吃饭的地方给做的. - 谢谢.
- Guy makes them where I always eat. - Thank you.

661
01:22:18,380 --> 01:22:20,970
我和布来希勒谈过 一起搭档的事.
I talked to Bressler about being on with me.

662
01:22:21,620 --> 01:22:24,240
等你出来继续和我干吧.
So you know you got a spot when you get out.

663
01:22:25,180 --> 01:22:28,280
我不知道我是否还回去.哈里.
I don't know if I am coming back, Harry.

664
01:22:30,140 --> 01:22:33,260
我仔细考虑了一下...
Doing a lot of thinking about it and...

665
01:22:36,500 --> 01:22:39,760
我还有个教师资格证.... 我的意思是...
I have a teaching credential. And I figure...

666
01:22:39,880 --> 01:22:41,910
...那是为什么? 你明白么?
...what for? You know?

667
01:22:45,680 --> 01:22:48,620
- 现在是治疗的时间了. - 你如今陷进去了.
- Time for therapy. - You hang in there now.

668
01:22:52,840 --> 01:22:53,040
再见,亲爱的.

669
01:22:54,560 --> 01:22:56,660
明天这个时候见.
See you tomorrow. Same time?

670
01:23:20,140 --> 01:23:22,840
- 你知道这是我的错. - 什么你的错?
- It's my fault, you know. - What?

671
01:23:23,360 --> 01:23:25,830
他的辞职. 我原以为我会无所谓...
His leaving. I thought I could take it.

672
01:23:25,830 --> 01:23:27,300
他不教书.
No class.

673
01:23:27,940 --> 01:23:30,100
- 不要那么说. - 为什么?
- Don't ever say that. - What?

674
01:23:30,700 --> 01:23:32,530
任何时候都不要对自己失望.
Don't ever low-rate yourself.

675
01:23:33,270 --> 01:23:36,970
我的意思是 无论如何作为一个警察的妻子...
What I meant was, whatever it takes to be a cop's wife...

676
01:23:37,100 --> 01:23:39,300
...我不知能否能够胜任.
...I'm just not sure I'm making it.

677
01:23:39,550 --> 01:23:42,080
他尽力了, 但是那些混蛋总是...
He really tries, and all these bastards...

678
01:23:42,080 --> 01:23:44,450
...鸡蛋里面挑骨头.
..."pig" this and "pig" that.

679
01:23:45,820 --> 01:23:49,620
或许我晚上看着他出门.
But maybe it's when I watch him walk out that door at night.

680
01:23:49,620 --> 01:23:50,920
我想...
And I think...

681
01:23:52,300 --> 01:23:54,790
...可能那是最后一次看到他!
...what if it's the last time I see him?

682
01:23:55,680 --> 01:23:57,280
就我一个人这样么?
Am I the only one?

683
01:23:57,680 --> 01:23:59,550
你的老婆不会吗?
Doesn't it drive your wife crazy?

684
01:23:59,550 --> 01:24:00,670
不.
No.

685
01:24:01,960 --> 01:24:04,080
她习惯了?
You mean she got used to it?

686
01:24:04,440 --> 01:24:06,370
不,她从没有习惯过,真的.
No, she never did, really.

687
01:24:06,740 --> 01:24:08,030
那为什么?
What then?

688
01:24:08,120 --> 01:24:09,450
她死了.
She's dead.

689
01:24:10,920 --> 01:24:12,690
对不起,原谅我.
Please, forgive me.

690
01:24:13,560 --> 01:24:16,850
她驾车回家的路上， 一个酒鬼驾车越过中线.
She was driving home and a drunk crossed the center line.

691
01:24:17,140 --> 01:24:18,540
没什么,真的.
No reason for it, really.

692
01:24:19,310 --> 01:24:21,610
- 我很抱歉. - 没关系.
- I'm so sorry. - That's okay.

693
01:24:22,360 --> 01:24:23,990
我要你告诉奇科...
I want you to tell Chico...

694
01:24:24,990 --> 01:24:27,250
...我理解他辞职.
...that I understand him quitting.

695
01:24:27,380 --> 01:24:30,510
他是对的. 这不是你们两个该过的生活.
I think he's right. This is no life for you two.

696
01:24:31,180 --> 01:24:34,310
- 那你为什么还干这行? - 我也不知道.
- Why do you stay in it, then? - I don't know.

697
01:24:36,020 --> 01:24:37,420
我真的不知道.
I really don't.

698
01:25:14,780 --> 01:25:17,040
给我一瓶五级的格莱姆酒. 稍等.
Let me have a 5th of Seagram's. Please.

699
01:25:18,180 --> 01:25:20,140
你怎么了?
What the hell happened to you?

700
01:25:20,140 --> 01:25:22,100
我妻子的兄弟干的
My wife's brother.

701
01:25:22,940 --> 01:25:24,030
我打了她...
I hit her...

702
01:25:24,500 --> 01:25:26,230
...他就揍了我.
...so he hit me.

703
01:25:26,230 --> 01:25:27,720
好几次了.
Several times.

704
01:25:29,160 --> 01:25:30,650
5.69美元.
$5.69.

705
01:25:32,680 --> 01:25:35,770
你是不是被抢了好几次了.
You're the guy that's been robbed all these times.

706
01:25:35,960 --> 01:25:38,460
最近三年里14次了.
14 times the last 3 years.

707
01:25:38,460 --> 01:25:41,480
不过最近两次混蛋们都是从担架上出去的.
Last 2 times, they sent them out here on platters.

708
01:25:41,760 --> 01:25:44,390
我枪法很棒.
I'm getting to be a pretty good shot.

709
01:25:45,680 --> 01:25:49,380
我总把它放在这. 就在这,很顺手.
And I always keep it right here. Right where it's handy.

710
01:25:49,780 --> 01:25:52,380
别开玩笑,我胆子小。
Please, I scare easy.

711
01:25:54,340 --> 01:25:57,310
贱货生的狗杂种！强盗！
Dirty son of a bitch! You pilferer!

712
01:26:34,840 --> 01:26:36,000
再见了.
Goodbye.

713
01:26:37,260 --> 01:26:39,050
明天见.
See you tomorrow.

714
01:26:49,180 --> 01:26:51,770
要下车的快点下.
Everybody out who gets out here?

715
01:26:51,940 --> 01:26:53,470
我是校车调查员。
School bus inspector.

716
01:26:53,600 --> 01:26:56,230
等一下.我没有权力让任何人包括...
One minute. I'm not allowed to have anybody...

717
01:26:56,230 --> 01:26:57,960
那我来授权你,快走.
I'm authorizing it, so go.

718
01:26:57,960 --> 01:26:59,760
你在干什么？ 我不认识你.
What are you doing? I don't know you.

719
01:26:59,760 --> 01:27:04,100
听着,老太婆,开车 否则用你的脑浆装饰这辆公车.
Hear me, old hag. Drive or I'll decorate this bus with your brains.

720
01:27:06,800 --> 01:27:10,390
- 那么去哪？ - 先开起来,我会告诉你去哪的.
- Where? - Just get started. I'll tell you where.

721
01:27:15,180 --> 01:27:16,800
现在我们来活跃一下气氛.
Let's have some fun now.

722
01:27:16,800 --> 01:27:18,330
谁会唱歌？
Who knows a song?

723
01:27:18,330 --> 01:27:21,520
每个人都会.你怎么样？ 你一定唱得很好听！
Everybody knows a song. You? You must know a beautiful one.

724
01:27:21,520 --> 01:27:23,310
来吧,唱一个给我们听听.
Come on, sing for us.

725
01:27:24,720 --> 01:27:27,190
老麦有个农场...
Old McDonald had a farm

726
01:27:27,300 --> 01:27:29,200
咿唉咿唉哦...
E-l-E-l-O

727
01:27:29,200 --> 01:27:32,040
农场上有一些鸭子...
And on his farm, he had some ducks.

728
01:27:32,800 --> 01:27:33,930
咿唉咿唉哦...
E-l-E-l-O

729
01:29:07,600 --> 01:29:11,500
- 爱丽,这位是探员科拉汉. - 哦,市长在等你们.
- Millie, this is Inspector Callahan. - The Mayor is waiting for you.

730
01:29:15,730 --> 01:29:18,420
- 发生了什么事？ - 那家伙又来信了.
- What's up? - Another note from our boy.

731
01:29:18,420 --> 01:29:22,520
- 他这次又绑架了谁？ - 那就是问题所在,还不知道会是谁.
- Who's he grabbed now? - That's the trouble, we don't know yet.

732
01:29:24,680 --> 01:29:27,440
飞机一定要在半小时内就绪.
The jet must be fueled and ready to go in 1/2 an hour.

733
01:29:28,000 --> 01:29:31,130
核心队员. 一定得是志愿者.
Skeleton crew. They must be volunteers.

734
01:29:31,620 --> 01:29:33,560
告诉他们那个人很危险.
Tell them the man is dangerous.

735
01:29:33,959 --> 01:29:37,689
这条消息是早上八点钟送来的 我念给你听.
I'll read you this note which was delivered at 8:00 this morning.

736
01:29:38,000 --> 01:29:42,260
“耍了我两次了的旧金山的市府， 这是最后一次...
"To the City of San Francisco...You double-crossed me for the last time.

737
01:29:42,580 --> 01:29:47,240
你警告你们,把我的20万 和喷气式飞机准备好.
"I'm warning you to have my $200,000 in a jet airplane ready and waiting.

738
01:29:47,940 --> 01:29:51,740
我会在一点打电话给市长 告诉你们人质的情况...
"I'll call the Mayor's office at 1:00 and tell you about the hostages...

739
01:29:52,080 --> 01:29:54,850
如果你们不按我说的办 我就杀了他们...
"...who I will be happy to kill if you don't do...

740
01:29:54,850 --> 01:29:57,120
"...严格按照我说的办.蝎子."
"...exactly what I say. Scorpio."

741
01:29:59,780 --> 01:30:01,870
最好严阵以待！
Better have somebody standing by!

742
01:30:02,880 --> 01:30:04,850
我不认为这是个无聊的的恶作剧.
I don't think it's a false alarm.

743
01:30:04,850 --> 01:30:07,080
市长先生,二号线有你的电话.
There's a call for you on line 2.

744
01:30:07,080 --> 01:30:09,550
我想就是你等的电话.
I think it's the one you've been waiting for.

745
01:30:16,060 --> 01:30:19,000
- 我是市长 - 我有公园大街小学的7个孩子
- It's the Mayor. - I got 7 kids from Park Street School.

746
01:30:19,760 --> 01:30:21,490
我有辆公车和...
I got the bus and...

747
01:30:21,490 --> 01:30:25,010
回去宝贝,回到车里去.真是个可爱的小姑娘.
Come on, honey, now back in the bus. That's a good girl.

748
01:30:25,109 --> 01:30:27,079
司机在我手上,她就在这.
I got the bus driver. Here she is.

749
01:30:27,079 --> 01:30:28,479
跟他说话.
Just tell him.

750
01:30:30,980 --> 01:30:32,450
不是我的错,他有枪...
Not my fault, he had a gun...

751
01:30:32,679 --> 01:30:33,699
告诉他们你的名字!
Just your name!

752
01:30:37,639 --> 01:30:39,169
我叫马塞拉-帕兰特.
This is Marcella Platt.

753
01:30:40,420 --> 01:30:43,450
如果你们想核实那就请便吧. 但是我想这无济于事.
You can check if you want. But I don't see any point.

754
01:30:43,450 --> 01:30:45,080
我不是在开玩笑.
I'm not bullshitting.

755
01:30:45,680 --> 01:30:48,670
听明白,我绑了孩子, 但你们如要到处设卡...
It's simple. I got the kids. You start screwing around...

756
01:30:48,670 --> 01:30:50,260
...孩子便会逐个死掉.
...the kids start dying.

757
01:30:50,439 --> 01:30:54,069
- 飞机准备好了吗？ - 正在加油,马上就好.
- The plane ready? - It's being fueled, and ready to go.

758
01:30:54,260 --> 01:30:57,060
你到之前,钱也会准备好.
The money will be there by the time you get there.

759
01:30:57,360 --> 01:31:00,660
听仔细了,我很快就到.
Listen carefully. I will drive along nice and easy.

760
01:31:00,660 --> 01:31:02,650
只有我和一车孩子.
Just me and a busload of kids.

761
01:31:02,650 --> 01:31:06,010
我会从瑟戴德拐到旧金山机场.
I'll turn off at Sir Drake Blvd., on my way to Santa Rosa Airport.

762
01:31:06,260 --> 01:31:07,990
我不想看见警车...
I don't want any police cars...

763
01:31:07,990 --> 01:31:09,250
...直升机,什么都不行.
...helicopters, whatever.

764
01:31:10,000 --> 01:31:14,160
如果你们按我说的办 这群孩子就会享受一次快乐的飞机旅行.
If you play this game by the rules, the kids will have a nice plane ride.

765
01:31:14,320 --> 01:31:16,010
你要带他们去哪？
Where are you going?

766
01:31:16,180 --> 01:31:18,850
上了飞机我会告诉驾驶员 不要害怕.
I'll tell the pilot when I get on. No alerts.

767
01:31:21,780 --> 01:31:25,040
我向你保证 你不会受到任何阻拦.
I guarantee you, you will not be molested in any way.

768
01:31:25,440 --> 01:31:26,990
以我的信誉担保.
I give you my word of honor.

769
01:31:27,300 --> 01:31:29,230
确认过了，有那个司机.
Marcella Platt. It checks.

770
01:31:30,520 --> 01:31:32,290
科拉汉?

771
01:31:33,959 --> 01:31:36,119
你打算把钱给他？
Willing to take the money to him?

772
01:31:36,860 --> 01:31:41,130
我们已经被他搅得够受了 这次该让他停手了.
When will you stop messing around with this guy? He has to be stopped now!

773
01:31:41,220 --> 01:31:44,280
他有一车的孩子做人质 我不敢冒这个险.
He's got a busload of kids and I can't take that chance.

774
01:31:44,940 --> 01:31:47,840
我已经向他保证 他不会受到阻挠.
I gave my word of honor and he will not be molested!

775
01:31:47,980 --> 01:31:49,740
这是命令！卡拉汉.
And that's a direct order!

776
01:31:50,860 --> 01:31:54,260
你另找个送货的人吧.
You can just get yourself another delivery boy.

777
01:33:16,120 --> 01:33:18,220
轻轻的划着小船...
Row, row, row your boat

778
01:33:18,520 --> 01:33:20,640
慢慢的顺着小溪...
Gently down the stream

779
01:33:20,880 --> 01:33:25,150
生活就像一场梦...
Merrily, merrily, merrily, merrily Life is but a dream

780
01:33:27,300 --> 01:33:29,130
我们要去哪？
Where are we going?

781
01:33:31,940 --> 01:33:35,640
- 这条路不对. - 我们要去冰淇淋工厂.
- This isn't the right way! - We're going to the ice cream factory.

782
01:33:35,800 --> 01:33:37,760
谁不愿意去就下车.
Anyone doesn't want to, can get off.

783
01:33:38,060 --> 01:33:40,650
我想回家找妈妈.
I want to go home to my mother.

784
01:33:40,780 --> 01:33:42,040
回家干什么？
Go home to your what?

785
01:33:42,040 --> 01:33:44,620
现在,唱首歌.再来一首.
Now, sing! Sing again!

786
01:33:48,640 --> 01:33:50,260
轻轻的划着小船...
Row, row, row your boat

787
01:33:44,980 --> 01:33:46,600
轻轻的划着小船...
Row, row, row your boat

788
01:33:46,600 --> 01:33:48,500
怎么回事？你这是唱歌么？
What's the matter? Don't you sing?

789
01:33:50,260 --> 01:33:52,490
你哪不舒服啊？怎么了？
Are you sick? What is it?

790
01:33:52,839 --> 01:33:55,429
唱，否则你妈妈就会死的！
Sing or your mothers will die!

791
01:33:56,080 --> 01:33:58,840
我会把你们妈妈和你们都杀了.
I'll kill your mothers! And the rest of you!

792
01:34:06,060 --> 01:34:07,990
走右手的通道.
Get in the right-hand lane.

793
01:34:08,340 --> 01:34:10,740
不能那样对待孩子.
Not right to treat children that way.

794
01:34:11,110 --> 01:34:13,670
- 你会伤害他们. - 开你的车吧！
- You'll hurt them. - Just drive the goddamn bus!

795
01:34:13,670 --> 01:34:15,730
走右手的通道！
And get in the right-hand lane!

796
01:34:22,660 --> 01:34:24,760
我要妈妈！
I want my mother.

797
01:34:33,159 --> 01:34:34,749
看到路标,斯达克布韦德.
The sign, Sir Drake Blvd.

798
01:34:35,040 --> 01:34:36,230
在那右转.
Make a right there.

799
01:34:40,640 --> 01:34:42,540
不是这里.
Not this one.

800
01:34:43,440 --> 01:34:44,840
我要妈妈.
I want my mother.

801
01:34:46,080 --> 01:34:46,810
闭上嘴！
Shut up!

802
01:34:49,280 --> 01:34:52,519
赶快右转.
Just get to the right!

803
01:35:07,500 --> 01:35:09,050
天啊！
Jesus!

804
01:35:14,900 --> 01:35:17,090
他到底在哪干什么？
What the hell is he doing up there?

805
01:35:22,020 --> 01:35:25,190
你到底在干什么？ 你能不能超过那辆大众车？
What the hell are you doing? Pass the V.W., will you?

806
01:38:45,300 --> 01:38:46,920
放下枪,趴下！
Drop the gun, creep!

807
01:38:48,860 --> 01:38:50,950
我会把他的头打烂！
I'll blow his brains out.

808
01:38:55,100 --> 01:38:56,820
把那该死的枪放下！
Drop the fucking gun!

809
01:39:44,160 --> 01:39:45,930
我知道你在想什么,人渣！
I know what your thinking, punk.

810
01:39:47,160 --> 01:39:50,590
"这个人是开了六枪还是五枪？
You're thinking: "Did he fire 6 shots, or only 5?"

811
01:39:51,239 --> 01:39:54,639
告你你吧,我太兴奋了,不记得了
To tell you the truth, I forgot myself, in all this excitement.

812
01:39:56,220 --> 01:39:59,950
但在我拿着这把44毫米口径的转轮手枪, 世界上威力最大的手枪...
But being this is a.44 Magnum, the most powerful handgun...

813
01:39:59,950 --> 01:40:02,750
...可以彻底打爆你的头情况下...
...and will blow your head clean off...

814
01:40:02,860 --> 01:40:04,820
...你该问问自己...
...you've got to ask yourself...

815
01:40:06,100 --> 01:40:07,860
...我今天走运么？...
..."Do I feel lucky?"

816
01:40:13,720 --> 01:40:15,950
你走运么,人渣？
Well, do you, punk?

